data.description:
The premier Hotel South Tampa & Suites Boutique is close to Tampa Bay Cruise Port, MacDill AFB. Visit hotelsouthtampa.com to Book Hotel in Tampa Bay Florida
We’re located just minutes from MacDill Airforce Base, the Port of Tampa, International Plaza and Westshore Mall, Tampa International Airport, downtown, Raymond James Stadium, Tampa General Hospital and the Tampa Bay Convention Center.

Wake up to our complimentary hot breakfast and stay connected with our free Wi-Fi internet access. Other amenities include our outdoor heated pool, fitness room and guest laundry. We also offer free parking for our overnight guests. Plus, Acaibar Enerjuicer is located at our hotel, and many other restaurants are within walking distance.

We look forward to welcoming you soon to Hotel South Tampa & Suites while looking for Hotel in Tampa Bay Florida!
